{"title": "Mess of Woe", "content": "\"I remember you dressed in pale blue silk at Mass one Easter morning, yes, like a lady wearing a\u2014piece of the\u2014weather! Oh, how proudly you walked, too proudly!\u2014But now you crouch and shuffle about barefooted; you live like a convict, dressed in the rags of a convict.\"\n\nA character is growing the Beard of Sorrow and indulging Drowning My Sorrows in his woe \u2014 both so seriously he Forgets to Eat (unless it involves pizza and/or ice cream, sometimes). Naturally, he's not going to be picking up after himself.\n\nMay overlap Men Can't Keep House, because this trope is more male than female. Can also involve Rage Against the Reflection.\n\nCompare Trash of the Titans, Seriously Scruffy and Room Full of Crazy. See also Skewed Priorities.", "url": "https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MessOfWoe", "media_links": ["/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/InsideNo9", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Theatre/TheRoseTattoo", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/XMenDaysOfFuturePast", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/PSILoveYou", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/ThorTheDarkWorld", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/YourServantMistress", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/GravePeril", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/SummerKnight", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheDresdenFiles", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/StephenKing", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/Misery", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/GottesBodenpersonal", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/BoredOfTheRings", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/TheBBC", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/TheMusketeers", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/BlackBooks", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/YoureTheWorst", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/WithoutATrace", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Theatre/TheRoseTattoo", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/DeusExHumanRevolution", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VisualNovel/RumblingHearts", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/MonsieurCharlatan", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/Ducktales2017", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/StevenUniverse"], "non_media_links":